## Return to Simpson's Paradox

We'll return to the Palmer penguins, and look at Simpson's paradox in Stan.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(palmerpenguins)
library(tidyverse)
library(cmdstanr)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr}
